<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ehsaas | तस्वीरों से परे</title>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;700;800&family=Rozha+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css"/>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">

    <style>
        .hindi-font { font-family: 'Rozha One', serif; }
        .eng-font { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
        
        /* Ensure text is hidden before animation starts */
        .reveal { opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards; }
        
        @keyframes stretchInX {
            from { transform: scaleX(0); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: scaleX(1); opacity: 1; }
        }
        .animate__stretchInX {
            animation-name: stretchInX;
            animation-duration: 1.5s;
            animation-timing-function: ease-out;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="gradient-bg min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-white relative overflow-hidden eng-font">

    <nav class="absolute top-0 w-full p-8 flex justify-center md:justify-start items-center animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">
        <div class="relative group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-60 transition duration-1000"></div>
            
            <div class="relative flex items-center gap-3 glass-card px-5 py-2 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl leading-none">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-tr from-pink-500 via-red-500 to-yellow-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-inner rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <span class="text-white font-black text-3xl italic">E</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pr-3">
                        <span class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter logo-text">EHSAAS</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="border-l border-white/20 pl-3 hidden sm:block">
                    <span class="text-indigo-100 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase opacity-80">अहसास मिलें</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="text-center px-6 z-10">
        <h1 class="hindi-font text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black mb-10 animate__animated animate__zoomInDown tracking-tighter leading-tight">
            तस्वीरें नहीं, <br> 
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-300 via-orange-300 to-white drop-shadow-lg">
                अहसास मिलें।
            </span>
        </h1>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="reveal hindi-font text-2xl md:text-4xl text-rose-50 italic animate__animated animate__fadeInUp animate__delay-1s">
                "कुछ अनसुनी बातें, कुछ अनकहे अहसास,"
            </p>
            
            <p class="reveal hindi-font text-2xl md:text-4xl text-rose-50 italic animate__animated animate__fadeInUp animate__delay-2s">
                "ढूंढलो उसे, जो हो तुम्हारे सबसे ख़ास।"
            </p>

            <div class="reveal h-[2px] w-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-yellow-200 to-transparent mx-auto my-8 animate__stretchInX animate__delay-3s"></div>

            <p class="reveal text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light text-white/80 leading-relaxed animate__animated animate__fadeIn animate__delay-4s">
                जहाँ कहानियाँ और यादें जुड़ती हैं। <br>
                <span class="tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-xs font-bold text-yellow-200/80">Ehsaas: Digital Soulmates</span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal mt-12 animate__animated animate__fadeInUp animate__delay-5s">
            <a href="/register" class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-10 py-5 bg-white text-pink-600 font-extrabold text-xl rounded-full shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(244,63,94,0.4)] hover:scale-110 hover:bg-rose-50 transition-all duration-500">
                सफ़र शुरू करें
                <span class="group-hover:translate-x-3 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>
                </span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] left-[-5%] w-96 h-96 bg-purple-600/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-[10%] right-[-10%] w-96 h-96 bg-yellow-400/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] animate-bounce" style="animation-duration: 10s;"></div>

</body>
</html>